            </div>
            <div class="col-7">
                <div class="row">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Family Owned</h2>
                    <h5 class="section-subtitle">Built on Tradition</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="pt-2">
                    <p>You can rely on our 20+ years of being a family run business, servicing Brisbane and surrounding areas</p>
                </div>
            </div>
